<br />
<br />LDQ #$01234567  ;;7 cycles
<br />STQ $00  ;;8 cycles
<br />
<br />15 cycles
<br />
<br />
<br />68000:
<br />
<br />MOVE.L #$01234567,(a0)  ;;20 cycles
<br />
<br />20 cycles

		

